data.description: This 3 bedroom and 2 bathroom home sits in a neighborhood. Entering the home you will notice the layout of the living room, featuring a wood burning stove. The kitchen offers wooden cabinetry, breakfast area and dinning room. Leading out the French doors in the breakfast area you will find a covered porch and fenced in back yard. The garage is ducted and wired. The home is also features a Generac generator.
